snippet.title: Josh Peck REACTS TO Drake Bell Pleading Guilty To MULTIPLE Charges!!! *IG LIVE*
snippet.description:
Josh Peck REACTS TO Drake Bell Pleading Guilty To MULTIPLE Charges!!! *IG LIVE*

We are all very much aware of the fact that cancel culture is one that is getting on everyone’s backs lately. Over the past couple of years, many celebrities have found themselves to be in the middle of some pretty interesting situations and one celebrity who has found themselves to be in quite a bit of trouble with cancel culture is in fact Drake Bell. It turns out the former Nickelodeon star pleaded guilty in regard to two different charges that are against him. During this virtual court appearance, things did not go all too well for the old childhood star and it seems that his ex-co star, Josh Peck, had quite a bit to say about it all.
